raft, a curse, and the mysterious deaths gave subtle elements of the supernatural. The descriptive imagery helped carry the story.\u003cbr\u003e\"the quiver of the moonbeams; they dance hand-in-hand with the shadows...\" pg. 241\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eOverall in enjoyed this story. The reading sometimes was tedious and slow but helped with the overall story. I would recommend this to anyone who enjoys a good story. Thanks!","rating":4,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/1986675?shelf=read"},"taggings":[{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"favorites","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/1986675?shelf=favorites"}},{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"american-literature","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/1986675?shelf=american-literature"}}],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2629894408"},"likeCount":69,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":4,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.7woQPc6MdrdvHPzXTH9FZw":{"id":"kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.7woQPc6MdrdvHPzXTH9FZw","__typename":"Book"},"User:31218670":{"id":31218670,"__typename":"User","legacyId":31218670,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1637690213i/31218670._UX200_CR0,0,200,200_.jpg","isAuthor":false,"textReviewsCount":265,"viewableName":"Olivia","isBlockedByViewer":false,"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/31218670-olivia","contributor":null,"isFollowing":false,"isFriend":false,"followersCount":51},"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.wwDojUIID78dn2tLvCwNLg":{"id":"kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.wwDojUIID78dn2tLvCwNLg","__typename":"Review","book":{"__ref":"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.7woQPc6MdrdvHPzXTH9FZw"},"creator":{"__ref":"User:31218670"},"recommendFor":null,"updatedAt":164341518